

This program computes the average luminance of each video file in a
collection of files. It also computes the minimum, maximum, mean
and median luminance value across all files.

Dependencies :

OpenCV - developed with version 3.3.0
Boost - developed with version 1.6.5.0

Usage:

calclum [directory of video files] [number of threads]

Example:

calclum /tmp/videoFiles 8

Would process the video files in the /tmp/videoFiles directory
using 8 video processing threads
